1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on congestion control and packet scheduling in the context of real-time video transmission, which is a key research area in networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with real-time video streaming, which is a key application area of multimedia research. 
3. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper deals with multipath transmission, which is a distributed computing problem. 
4. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper uses utility maximization theory, which is a key concept in information theory. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with congestion control and packet scheduling, which are control problems in systems and control research.
